		<section id="H4B3D86B3824844F2B1FC6C8DC3E308A1" section-type="section-one">
      <enum>1.</enum>
      <header>Short title</header>
      <text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the
			 <quote>
          <short-title>The Bureau of Corrections Renaming Act
			 of 2013</short-title>
        </quote>.</text>
		</section>
    <section id="H26D94216FEEC4FA8A72CBD18B58BB377" section-type="subsequent-section">
      <enum>2.</enum>
      <header>Renaming of Bureau of
			 Prisons</header>
			<subsection id="HBB728A4F917B4EA5AC80800E2F7D34A5">
        <enum>(a)</enum>
        <header>In
			 general</header>
        <text>The <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" entity-id="1540">Bureau of Prisons in the Department of Justice</cato:entity-ref> is
			 renamed the <term>
            <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" value="Bureau of Corrections" entity-id="1540" proposed="true">Bureau of Corrections</cato:entity-ref>
          </term>.</text>
			</subsection>
