			 other references to Bureau of Prisons</header>
        <text>Each reference to the
			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" entity-id="1540">Bureau of Prisons</cato:entity-ref> in the laws and regulations of the United States, other than
